{"tid":1014891,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【開心速遞】傻強被Out冇得愛回家　馮奕森交代去向：我不會回頭","createTime":"2019-02-09T14:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T10:33:24.000Z","uid":71166,"like":104,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7d6268cba7c43206c6e4b74997e3c60749ae7197","tid":1014891,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"甫踏入2019年無耐，無綫處境劇《愛‧回家之開心速遞》雖然會添食加拍至720集，但就有人氣角色相繼離開劇組，繼博士（馬貫東飾）與Mandy（謝芷倫飾）因為拍其他劇而要離「家」之外，早前就連傻強 (馮奕森飾) 都無得留低，他今次更是無聲無色地被Out走，劇情突然講述傻強去西伯利亞留學了，甚至連講拜拜道別的機會都無。網民紛紛表示好唔捨得傻強，又留言追問原因，大呼：「還我傻強！」不過馮奕森對於自己無得再拍該劇的原因並沒有透露半句，不禁惹來各種揣測。<br />\n<br />\n傻強一角明明深受觀眾同網民歡迎，其戇直搞笑的丑角形像深入民心，去年曾經有一段時間他的戲份亦明顯多了，正當大家覺得傻強慢慢開始上位，想不到他卻突然被「消失」。而剛巧他早前客串演出的FOX劇集《心冤》播映了，飾演警察的他只於第一集有份出鏡，且只有幾秒的鏡頭和一句對白，不過就好大機會是因為這短短的幾秒戲份，而令他觸怒了TVB。事實是《心冤》第一集播出後不久，他就無得再演出《愛‧回家》，未知是巧合，還是他真的因此得罪了方丈。之前江嘉敏也曾因為接拍了ViuTV的劇集《三一如三》而激嬲了TVB，遭掟入雪櫃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨晚馮奕森終於開腔回應被飛一事，他說：「其實對於《愛‧回家》我亦都無咩嘢可以回答，我只能夠講一切有最好嘅安排，我依然係喺公司，依然都係活躍嘅，大家會繼續喺電影框上面見到我嘅，我人係安好嘅，無事無事，大家放心。演員路真係唔易行，當中有風都有沙，我有責任時人哋亦有責任，互相都有責任，所有嘢都可以做得更加好，更加盡善盡美嘅，我亦都希望嚟緊嘅日子會有更好嘅performance畀大家睇，依然會等待一個更好嘅角色。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他又感恩公司給他演出傻強的機會：「其實公司對我好好嘅，高層都對我好好嘅，佢哋都體諒我，肯畀我演呢個咁爆嘅角色，傻強帶咗畀我好多嘢，但沒有最好只有更好，我都希望有更多嘅嘗試。」始終未有透露真正的原因，笑言：「要講原因有十萬個嘅，總之我會一直走，不回頭，期待有更好嘅演出。」他表示現正在放大假，稍後將會演出新劇《十八年後的終極告白》：「唔算太多戲份但個角色突出嘅，我做陳山聰嘅頭馬，到時大家可以留意下。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2418512/org/9376baf0641a9e6f87385dcca2ce3906.jpg/SFeckWPKOWESgZTx6jDDK7pujDAqWrOPO2I4tjtiOLY?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2418512%2Forg%2F9376baf0641a9e6f87385dcca2ce3906.jpg%2FSFeckWPKOWESgZTx6jDDK7pujDAqWrOPO2I4tjtiOLY%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=bded9321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傻強已正式離開咗《愛‧回家》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2418518/org/273c68bd47a6353792bcfb51c717087f.jpg/1IY7vSB7ZRDYXV1R_uaT7QGpHhd8zC2dzSmVqc0plak?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2418518%2Forg%2F273c68bd47a6353792bcfb51c717087f.jpg%2F1IY7vSB7ZRDYXV1R_uaT7QGpHhd8zC2dzSmVqc0plak%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=4bbb152c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都好唔捨得傻強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2418522/org/921148d39e3053da379c860655467db1.jpg/KOKtpY7vsMyvQTnUeTg2pXt1an3pjA9DwCqXNcAqlzU?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2418522%2Forg%2F921148d39e3053da379c860655467db1.jpg%2FKOKtpY7vsMyvQTnUeTg2pXt1an3pjA9DwCqXNcAqlzU%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=bbd80316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馮奕森於FOX嘅劇集《心冤》客串演出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2418528/org/862d293884e6dfdd2c07e2864fc1b3a9.jpg/hiJQUNce4VptLQhPdLFatnQwmDtqH6D4k61f5JOtX-Q?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2418528%2Forg%2F862d293884e6dfdd2c07e2864fc1b3a9.jpg%2FhiJQUNce4VptLQhPdLFatnQwmDtqH6D4k61f5JOtX-Q%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=6d98a09c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話一切有最好嘅安排。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2418544/org/ebfc25cab1b2cefca4abd928da15adf6.jpg/MCIutA8b7o0U7Nl47hrCtLmEnku7u7IgYkGG_2JBhv8?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2418544%2Forg%2Febfc25cab1b2cefca4abd928da15adf6.jpg%2FMCIutA8b7o0U7Nl47hrCtLmEnku7u7IgYkGG_2JBhv8%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=b39aef18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話傻強呢個角色帶畀佢好多嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/292825/開心速遞-傻強被out冇得愛回家-馮奕森交代去向-我不會回頭\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F292825%2F%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E-%E5%82%BB%E5%BC%B7%E8%A2%ABout%E5%86%87%E5%BE%97%E6%84%9B%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6-%E9%A6%AE%E5%A5%95%E6%A3%AE%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%A3%E5%8E%BB%E5%90%91-%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%9B%9E%E9%A0%AD&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jIyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=ea30fea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/292825/開心速遞-傻強被out冇得愛回家-馮奕森交代去向-我不會回頭</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強強  我拾不得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43aa64cbf5869c3ecc02b5d51aff1ba2cb04124","tid":1014891,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"十八年後的終極告白唔係拍撚完啦咩"},{"pid":"2a881672128f29b4cb4e767ff04a597af032e3d2","tid":1014891,"uid":555,"like":20,"dislike":74,"score":-54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦 唔使見到佢仲好"},{"pid":"ae6713c1b949a2a7fa22cdaf6b8ea827e41838c9","tid":1014891,"uid":228963,"like":15,"dislike":52,"score":-37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42b65100c3906e2e7ceaf4733691500ae3d1044b","tid":1014891,"uid":182556,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2yj5Kx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2yj5Kx.png&h=e1482ebc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abe3b6b13cf99df4eb9bffd65bf3027a06aa7431","tid":1014891,"uid":142532,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"3638f577e1a16ed2f1156cde4cfa4685f4e59347","tid":1014891,"uid":39608,"like":7,"dislike":27,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"想睇隻鬼回歸"},{"pid":"7e028c5419f5d883fba1513b7a7d21e732bb5c67","tid":1014891,"uid":71166,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:43:58.000Z","msg":"強強真係好硬頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb467aed325d326c24d94e31e1b91ff85eabfe0","tid":1014891,"uid":7116